OL,3,CWater supplies 'restored' after Conwy
OL,4,Cburst pipe incident
OL,6,FWater supplies have been fully
OL,7,Frestored to homes affected by a major
OL,8,Fdisruption in Conwy County according
OL,9,Fto Welsh Water but there are still
OL,10,Freports of disruption in the area.
OL,12,FThe outage began last week after a
OL,13,Fburst pipe at the Bryn Cowlyd Water
OL,14,FTreatment Works in Dolgarrog left some
OL,15,Fcommunities without water for a fourth
OL,16,Fconsecutive day.
OL,18,FOn Monday morning Welsh Water
OL,19,Fconfirmed the network has now refilled
OL,20,Fand water supplies have been restored.
