OL,4,Cburst pipe incident
OL,6,FIt sayid all affected schools are now
OL,7,Fback on supply and alternative water
OL,8,Fsupplies will continue to be in place
OL,9,Ftoday.
OL,11,FHowever Conwy Council said at least
OL,12,Fseven schools are still closed due to
OL,13,Fa lack of water supplies.
OL,15,FPeople in the area have told ITV News
OL,16,Fthey are aware of some households with
OL,17,Fjust 'a trickle' of water coming from
OL,18,Ftheir taps.
