OL,3,CWater supplies 'restored' after Conwy
OL,4,Cburst pipe incident
OL,6,FWelsh Water said it had already
OL,7,Fconfirmed the compensation
OL,8,Farrangements for our household and
OL,9,Fbusiness customers and apologised
OL,10,Fagain for the inconvenience
OL,11,Fexperienced by customers
OL,13,FThe burst pipe, which is believed to
OL,14,Fhave impacted around 40,000 properties
OL,15,Fsince Wednesday, has caused
OL,16,Fsignificant disruption, including the
OL,17,Fclosure of schools and businesses in
OL,18,Fthe area.
