OL,3,CWater supplies 'restored' after Conwy
OL,4,Cburst pipe incident
OL,6,FAlthough the main leak at the
OL,7,Ftreatment plant was repaired on Friday
OL,8,Fafternoon, Welsh Water warned it could
OL,9,Ftake up to 48 hours for the supply to
OL,10,Ffully stabilise and return to normal
OL,11,Ffor all affected homes.
OL,13,FOver the weekend, the utility company
OL,14,Ffocused on repairing several smaller
OL,15,Fleaks and bursts, with engineers
OL,16,Fworking through the night to help
OL,17,Frepressurise the system that had
OL,18,Femptied.
